  "texts": [
    "These obtained values indicate that batch size has a P-value < 0.05, indicating a departure from normality.",
    "Both the learning rate and the dropout period have a P-value > 0.05, suggesting normality.",
    "Figure 7 shows the distribution of accuracy values for the dropout period, learning rate, and batch size.",
    "As can be observed, the normality of the learning rate is very obvious.",
    "These results are consistent to the obtained P-values of Shapiro-Wilk."
